Database folder structure for

The following file contains scripts to download all the database files required for
the viral discovery pipeline to work.

Required executables in PATH:
	1. wget
	2. tar and gunzip
	3. GNU sed
	4. bwa (for GRCh38 index building)
	5. stampy.py (for GRCh38 index building)
	6. makeblastdb (blast+ ; for Refseq Viral blastdb building)
	7. hmmpress (HMMER suite: http://hmmer.janelia.org/ ; for Pfam and vFam  .hmm databases )
	8. kraken-build (from Kraken software: https://ccb.jhu.edu/software/kraken/ )
